{"name":"Weapon Mastery","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-compendium/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 59\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><em>Mastery</em> of one weapon (+1 &ldquo;to hit&rdquo; and +1 damage). Additional weapons may be mastered at 4th, 8th, and 12th levels. As noted in <strong>Chapter 6: Equipment</strong>, the attack rate for melee weapons and the rates of fire for most missile weapons improve through <em>weapon mastery</em>. For more information on <em>weapon mastery</em>, see <strong>Chapter 9: Combat</strong>, <em>weapon skill</em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"warlock","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679250294860,"modifiedTime":1681579210132,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"sEJUGkIL5NkTj3nt","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
